{"tid":715569,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"近年有冇乜RPG game仲比得上the last of us","createTime":"2018-06-24T14:52:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-25T10:25:42.000Z","uid":50620,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"fb561e45a56a8f52943d870932a8d73ce684adcd","tid":715569,"uid":50620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T14:52:09.000Z","msg":"P5，Zelda，人中系列，dark souls，bb ，nier等等之類我都有玩<br />\n以上我都超鍾意<br />\n<br />\n但the last of us嘅劇情，人物，情景，音樂，節奏，玩法細節都做得好出色<br />\n<br />\n我地玩完會明joel點解有咁嘅選擇<br />\nEllie最後一幕個坦白<br />\nMarlene 點解明明要保護ellie都選擇做手術<br />\n甚至會代入其中，同情每個角色嘅處境<br />\n依d都係營造角色成功先達到效果<br />\n<br />\n而每章故事嘅人都令人深刻<br />\n黑人兄弟個故事，一定玩過嘅人而家都會記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n要讚嘅地方太多，未玩過就買黎玩，玩過一定有同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大家繼續一齊期待下一集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/btmN-bWwv0A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FbtmN-bWwv0A&d=%2B07ZEybtJ%2Fh79VOJ5xHweeargVTjPUnXFlgjsLUvQ6w%3D&h=4d88e5bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/btmN-bWwv0A</a>"},{"pid":"23806776216c0f3797423b485e37a6dbe0062a2c","tid":715569,"uid":94835,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T14:54:23.000Z","msg":"依隻係rpg咩"},{"pid":"d72c9f37a6183c6427c8f9c7690046e9e70956cd","tid":715569,"uid":1495,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T14:54:45.000Z","msg":"rpg<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1232545c8564ac3923461a1760dcbeefa859892d","tid":715569,"uid":187729,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-24T14:55:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58a8d5185146e13bf94ad58b2cd72c48dcc84cb5","tid":715569,"uid":181875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor